\nJupiter-mass planets with an eccentric model when there is no evidence of\nnon-circularity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 May 2011 19:20:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Apr 2012 15:11:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
