nd of $\\Omega(n^{3})$ on the transience\nclass on the grid improving the obvious bound of $\\Omega(n^{2})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 May 2011 13:25:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2012 18:07:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2012 16:58:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-17"}
